  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN165-kilavi">makaṭpōkkiya <app><lem>tāy</lem><rdg wit="#C7 #RK">tāyatu</rdg></app> <app><lem>nilai</lem><rdg wit="#C7 #C9">nilaimai</rdg><rdg wit="#C9">nilaimai kaṇṭu</rdg><rdg wit="#C5">nilaiyaik</rdg></app> kaṇṭār colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">What the onlookers said about the state of the mother who had let [her] daughter go.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN165">
        <l><anchor n="1"/>kayantalai maṭappiṭi <supplied>pa</supplied>yampiṟ paṭṭeṉak</l>
        <l>kaḷiṟuviḷip paṭutta kampalai verīi</l>
        <l>yoyyeṉa veḻunta cevvāyk kuḻavi</l>
        <l>tāteru maṟukiṉ mūtū rāṅ<supplied>ka</supplied></l>
        <l>ṇerumai nallāṉ perumulai māntu</l>
        <l>nāṭupala viṟanta naṉ<supplied>ṉa</supplied> rāṭṭik</l>
        <l>kāyamu maṇiyiḻan taḻuṅkiṉṟu tāyu</l>
        <l>miṉṟō ṭārā yiṟīiyareṉ ṉuyireṉak</l>
        <l>kaṇṇu nutalu nīvit taṇṇeṉat</l>
        <l>taṭavunilai nocci variniḻa lacaiit</l>
        <l>tāḻik kuvaḷai vāṭumalar cūṭit</l>
        <l>tarumaṇaṟ kiṭanta pāvaiyeṉ</l>
        <l>marumaka ḷēyeṉa muyaṅkiṉa ḷaḻumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Because of the good woman who has gone to traverse many lands, (6)</l>
        <l>where the red-mouthed calf that has suddenly risen, (3)</l>
        <l>frightened by the clamour caused by the elephant bull’s calls, (2)</l>
        <l>because [his] soft-headed youthful cow has fallen into a pit, (1)</l>
        <l>feeds from the big teats of the good buffalo cow, (5)</l>
        <l>there by the old village with streets of dusty dung (4)</l>
        <l>[her] companions’ ornaments are lost [and] spoilt, and [her] mother (6)</l>
        <l>cries, one who embraces as [her] daughter-in-law (13)</l>
        <l>the doll that lies in the sand that was brought, (12)</l>
        <l>stroking [her] eyes and forehead with the words (8a-c)</l>
        <l>“give [me your] sweet shoulders. May my life break!”, (7)</l>
        <l>resting coolly in the dappled shade of the broad-trunked Nocci tree, (9d-10)</l>
        <l>putting on [her] the fading blossoms of potted waterlilies. (11)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>

